Eng Trans @ThesignIDF

467
00:38:01,570 --> 00:38:08,550
The Sign

468
00:38:39,751 --> 00:38:42,839
King Garuda, why are you here?

469
00:38:45,636 --> 00:38:46,886
Why did you help me?

470
00:38:47,129 --> 00:38:49,519
You were still alive so I decided to help.

471
00:38:50,946 --> 00:38:53,449
On the 15th day of the 11th month...

472
00:38:53,449 --> 00:39:01,711
all the Nagas and Naginis as well as their attendants will present their offerings and breathe out the fireballs as an act of worship.

473
00:39:02,757 --> 00:39:04,179
Beautiful, isn’t it?

474
00:39:05,637 --> 00:39:06,789
Yes.

475
00:39:08,414 --> 00:39:09,479
So beautiful.

476
00:39:11,969 --> 00:39:13,559
I can’t go with you.

477
00:39:13,911 --> 00:39:15,819
I don’t want anyone to die because of me.

478
00:39:18,419 --> 00:39:20,951
Master Sakunanoparuj, this way.

479
00:39:29,500 --> 00:39:31,889
Phaya!

480
00:39:32,460 --> 00:39:33,719
Phaya!

481
00:39:34,226 --> 00:39:35,403
Phaya!

482
00:39:39,169 --> 00:39:40,786
What happened?

483
00:39:40,797 --> 00:39:41,631
Ouch.

484
00:39:45,449 --> 00:39:49,866
I was trying to get the book and the pile just tumbled down.

485
00:39:51,031 --> 00:39:53,159
Are you all right?

486
00:39:55,309 --> 00:39:57,111
Yeah.

487
00:39:58,877 --> 00:40:01,803
I ran here as soon as I heard the noise...

488
00:40:01,803 --> 00:40:03,799
and saw you lying unconcious on the floor.

489
00:40:03,909 --> 00:40:08,146
It took quite some time to wake you up. I was so worried.

490
00:40:09,082 --> 00:40:13,209
I’m so sorry. Your room is a mess now.

491
00:40:13,863 --> 00:40:16,157
- Let me help you tidy up.
- It’s all right.

492
00:40:17,106 --> 00:40:17,883
Ouch!

493
00:40:26,269 --> 00:40:28,229
(The Son of Naga City Governor)

494
00:40:43,749 --> 00:40:48,197
Wi, can I borrow this book for a while?

495
00:40:49,349 --> 00:40:50,220
Sure.

496
00:40:51,386 --> 00:40:52,254
Thank you.

497
00:41:06,939 --> 00:41:11,923
Oh, hello Doc. Why didn’t you tell me you’d be here today?

498
00:41:12,499 --> 00:41:14,506
My patient just cancelled the appointment.

499
00:41:14,989 --> 00:41:17,226
So, I’m thinking maybe we could go out for dinner.

500
00:41:17,729 --> 00:41:19,214
Do you want to join me?

501
00:41:19,843 --> 00:41:25,849
Sure. Please come and wait in my room first.

502
00:41:26,146 --> 00:41:27,666
I’ll go get changed.

503
00:41:29,094 --> 00:41:29,723
Okay.

504
00:41:29,929 --> 00:41:30,843
Please come in.

505
00:41:53,414 --> 00:41:54,306
Where are you going?

506
00:41:56,020 --> 00:41:57,837
He’s going to have dinner with me.

507
00:41:58,797 --> 00:41:59,871
Do you need anything?

508
00:42:01,837 --> 00:42:03,551
I’m afraid he can’t go with you now.

509
00:42:04,054 --> 00:42:04,991
Because he’s coming with me.

510
00:42:05,837 --> 00:42:07,437
Come with me, Tharn.

511
00:42:08,329 --> 00:42:09,677
Hang on.

512
00:42:11,026 --> 00:42:12,923
Did I say I’d go with you?

513
00:42:13,414 --> 00:42:15,254
But I have something important to talk to you.

514
00:42:18,626 --> 00:42:20,340
You have no rights to force him.

515
00:42:21,986 --> 00:42:23,711
This is outside of your working hours.

516
00:42:25,231 --> 00:42:27,666
My job is to take care of him.

517
00:42:28,831 --> 00:42:30,180
But I don’t want to go with you.

518
00:42:34,683 --> 00:42:39,266
Do you remember when I warned you that you might be in danger?

519
00:42:39,711 --> 00:42:42,077
I told you to stay beside me so that I can protect you.

520
00:42:42,340 --> 00:42:45,986
But I’m going with Doc. It’s not dangerous at all.

521
00:42:48,989 --> 00:42:49,843
Tharn.

522
00:42:58,229 --> 00:43:00,289
If you are really worried about him...

523
00:43:00,631 --> 00:43:02,346
you’d better stay away from him.

524
00:43:03,917 --> 00:43:05,849
The closer you get to him,

525
00:43:07,176 --> 00:43:09,003
the more danger he’d be in.

526
00:43:12,090 --> 00:43:14,146
The one who actually puts him in danger...

527
00:43:15,209 --> 00:43:16,237
is probably not me.

528
00:43:16,229 --> 00:43:17,506
But I think it is.

529
00:43:19,504 --> 00:43:23,837
Since the day you met him, he has to risk his life to save you for so many times.

530
00:43:25,587 --> 00:43:28,054
If he were to die,

531
00:43:29,984 --> 00:43:32,089
you’re most likely to be the cause of it.

532
00:43:32,089 --> 00:43:33,414
What the fuck are you talking about?!

533
00:43:33,409 --> 00:43:34,329
Ouch!!

534
00:43:38,149 --> 00:43:40,500
Just because he thinks of you as his big brother...

535
00:43:41,047 --> 00:43:42,546
doesn’t mean that I’d be afraid of you.

536
00:43:43,906 --> 00:43:48,107
I don’t really give a fuck about anything!

537
00:43:48,435 --> 00:43:49,369
Phaya!

538
00:43:54,774 --> 00:43:56,614
You mark my words.

539
00:43:58,222 --> 00:44:01,963
I will do everything to keep you two apart.

540
00:44:02,637 --> 00:44:04,397
I will take him away from you.

541
00:44:06,024 --> 00:44:08,249
Even if he has to die.

542
00:44:09,655 --> 00:44:10,557
What the fuck!!

543
00:44:10,549 --> 00:44:11,369
(Punching)

544
00:44:12,054 --> 00:44:13,413
Are you all right?

545
00:44:14,450 --> 00:44:16,389
Tharn, come with me.

546
00:44:16,389 --> 00:44:17,986
Come with me, Tharn.

547
00:44:17,979 --> 00:44:19,094
Let me go!

548
00:44:19,089 --> 00:44:19,997
(Punching)
Ouch!

549
00:44:33,400 --> 00:44:34,934
What’s wrong with you?!

550
00:44:39,631 --> 00:44:40,774
Let’s go.

551
00:44:53,083 --> 00:44:54,203
Damn it!

552
00:45:03,409 --> 00:45:07,151
I’m so sorry that he hurt you.

553
00:45:08,069 --> 00:45:12,511
It’s okay. He’s probably very worried about you.

554
00:45:14,477 --> 00:45:16,831
I don’t know what’s got into him.

555
00:45:17,357 --> 00:45:19,551
But it makes me want to stay away from him from now on.

556
00:45:27,917 --> 00:45:31,948
Your inspector wants me to find out more information on Lieutenant Tam’s case.

557
00:45:33,050 --> 00:45:33,862
Okay

558
00:45:34,393 --> 00:45:37,342
Didn't you guys already know this?

559
00:45:37,429 --> 00:45:44,429
The Sign
